	[Noting Rob's changes from earlier this week]
	* src/main/perl/lib/BLM/DBHandler.pm (dbi): New attribute
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/Context.pm
	(cgi_header_in): Updates for Apache 2.2 compatibility
	(cgi_header_out): ditto
	* src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/Apache/Bedrock.pm
	(Apache2::Const): use
	(NOT_FOUND): replaced hard-coded value with value from Apache2::Const
	(SERVER_ERROR): likewise
	(FORBIDDEN): likewise
	(OK): likewise
	(DECLINED): likewise
	(REDIRECT): new constant
	(config): removed unnecessary warn statements (dev. debugging msgs)
	(page_name): whitespace changes only
	(handler): Added Apache 2 hack for redirection
	* NEWS: Mentioned above in 2.0.5 news section

