	CVS transplanted following files from tree rooted at
	Perl/Bedrock. Note that the subtree formerly at:
	    Perl/Bedrock/BLM
	has been migrated to:
	    src/main/perl/lib/BLM
	and /not/:
	    src/main/perl/lib/Bedrock/BLM
	This is to reflect the package names of the BLM modules, which are
	    BLM::Foo
	not
	    Bedrock::BLM::Foo
